(66572, '0A6FA242-FBCE-4DBF-BC17-FAA953E7B650', 'I️ understand that you want that clarity. It’s nebulous intentionally and he’s not going to do any more digging for it. He has enough clarity to make him feel comfortable doing what he’s doing. And quite honestly, he gets to make that decision and so do I️. This isn’t the way you’re going to get to feel comfortable. I’m not signing up for ethical non monogamy. I’m signing up for getting joy from people I️ adore and have pre-existing connection with.  Sadly love this is our impasse and I️ don’t think we are going to resolve it this way.   I have deep curiosity about why what Ramy does matters SO very much to you. If you heard he was cheating on his wife with someone else, would you work to stop it. Or would you work to stop anyone you knew who was cheating. You aren’t consenting to anything and you aren’t committing any pain. These are not your relationships. I wonder why you can’t disconnect from it a bit more. It’s a genuine curisoity I️ have. ', '699319180522345984', '699319243319379072', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'E:nwdave@b-zb.com', '+19172390518', '2023-02-28T15:19:40.522346'),
