(66589, '1EF84243-3A3E-43B6-89E1-EAD289EBB013', 'I️ have thoughts love on this and have considered this…many times. I️ have grappled with this exact question for many years. We come to different conclusions. We are now in the territory where I️’m worried we are trying to convince each other of our POV. My question was genuine. I️ want to know why you care so much about what I️ do or what Ramy does when you have nothing to do with it. Asking me to imagine the pain of someone else is not the same kind of curiosity exercise. But if you want the answer, it’s why I️ told you I️ was cheating and wanted to start over (albeit terribly not the right way of telling you). But I️’m not in a place to make that decision for others. ', '699322661199777664', '699322669834832384', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'E:nwdave@b-zb.com', '+19172390518', '2023-02-28T16:17:41.199778'),
