(66614, '5B172BC2-3497-475C-814C-489651071DFE', 'I️’m sending you gratitude from this car ride to the airport to say that I️ really appreciated our conversation last night. I️ can see that we are both trying hard to find a new way through this and we’re both finding places to bend. It felt good to have a grounded, collaborative, creative and regulated conversation. I️’m sorry I️ couldn’t muster the energy for a sexual connection as I️ was feeling super anxious about how little sleep I️ was getting. Then of course orli woke me up twice in the three hours I️ had to sleep. Argh. But I️’m grateful to be headed to nyc in a better place with you. I️ can’t wait to be home in your arms again this weekend and to lean into learning something new this Saturday.', '699369839267119616', '699372443540439552', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'E:nwdave@b-zb.com', '+19172390518', '2023-03-01T05:23:59.267120'),
(66624, '527AE821-115D-4496-8CE1-589E1C02D388', 'Hey love, I hope you are resting on the plane. Yes, thank you for last night. I appreciate you coming into the conversation with an offer to close down Garrett from future non-monogamy explorations and for helping me consider other narratives. I know you have been in enormous pain from me built up over months. I had hit bottom and am still feeling very shaky and a bit confused. I’m happy to have a few days to rest, process and regroup. I understand everything you are Saying about not being able to be sexual last night. I was disappointed…in the spirit of being explicit about my needs, In those moment when we have made enormous efforts and progress to rebuild our connection, I do need the physical intimacy to let it sink in…my body really needs to experience the closeness with you for it to sink in and feel real and lasting….especially given the 10 day gap, the disruption with Garrett and now the prospect of you being with Ramy. I felt like I was waiting for you (shower, packing, work emails, soccer sign up) and after all that….of course you felt too tired. I didn’t know if you felt enough connection to go there and my learning is….I should have asked you or just joined you when you were in the shower. My request of you is to help prioritize sex in similar moments…when there aren’t any emotional blockers and you feel at least open. I know you are always happy when we do, and it really helps me on an emotional and somatic level. I feel left a bit hanging….and I need all the lift I can get right now. ', '699380609113253376', 'None', 1, 'David', 'Nitzan', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'E:nwdave@b-zb.com', 'David', '2023-03-01T08:23:29.113253'),
